ibuilds. Every package in NixOS is defined with Nix config files, and		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ithe Nix package manager can promise that, as long as the software		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
idoesn't deliberately fight back, you will get binaries with the exact		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
isame functionality, and in most cases, get binaries with the same hash		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ivalues (such as MD5 and SHA256).		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
